To run this program you need to create database first, here you have database.sql with tables needed.
Also you have to setup the configuration for connection in Database class in getConnection method.
After that if you dont have driver it will throw an error, so you have to import jdbc driver
Link for download: https://dev.mysql.com/downloads/connector/j/5.1.html.

There are still small bugs that needed to be fixed till final duedate but nothing that will affect workflow of
program.